sellerAgent.name: Dalton Carroll of the Lionheart Group

data.description:
Step into this stunning, recently renovated home flooded with natural light. The heart of the home is the bright and modern kitchen, all appliances were purchased in 2021, making it ideal for food enthusiasts.  This well thought-out floor plan provides 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths. This well-designed layout offers three bedrooms and two full bathrooms. Each room boasts ample natural light, recessed lighting, and contemporary fixtures throughout the entire home. The garage has been transformed, now featuring additional shelving space. 
Updates from 2021-2022 include: kitchen cabinets, flooring, carpet, windows, HVAC, hot water heater, electrical panel, repaired plumbing, fence.
As an added bonus, all fixtures, appliances, security cameras and the custom-built desk in the office will be included with the property.
